public abstract class PE
extends GridPredicate<GridEvent>

Defines alias for GridPredicate<GridEvent> by extending GridPredicate. Since Java doesn't provide type aliases (like Scala, for example) we resort to these types of measures. This is intended to provide for more concise code without sacrificing readability. For more information see GridPredicate and GridEvent.
